ion Nutrition through Personalized Supplementation Plans? - April 2024&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#factors-to-take-into-account-when-interpreting-25-hydroxy-vitamin-d-serum-levels--march-2024&#34;&gt;Factors to take into account when interpreting 25-hydroxy-vitamin D serum levels – March 2024&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#perhaps-100x-difference-in-blood-level-responses-to-identical-vitamin-d-dosing&#34;&gt;Perhaps 100X difference in BLOOD-Level responses to identical Vitamin D dosing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#perhaps-a-500x-difference-in-cell-level-responses-to--identical-vitamin-d-dosing&#34;&gt;Perhaps a 500X difference in CELL-Level responses to  identical Vitamin D dosing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;23-personalization-factors-for-vitamin-d-treatment&#34;&gt;23+ Personalization factors for Vitamin D treatment:&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Body size: less for youths, &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/overview-obesity-and-vitamin-d&#34; style=&#34;color: red; text-decoration: underline;&#34; title=&#34;This post/category does not exist yet: Overview Obesity and Vitamin D&#34;&gt;more for obese&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
